import React from 'react' import './ExpenseItem.css' function ExpenseItem(props) { //props can be named anything .. const expenseDate=props.date; //it is an object with properties as mentioned in app.js attributes const expenseTitle=props.title; const expenseAmount=props.amount; return (
{expenseDate.toISOString()}

{expenseTitle}

${expenseAmount}
) } export default ExpenseItem
